  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In cases where full objects contain signatures (currently only `BeaconBlock`s), the `signing_root` is used as a summary instead of the `hash_tree_root`. The definition of a summary should be expanded (lol) to include this edge case.\r\n\r\neg:\r\na block header:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  slot: Slot,\r\n  parent_root: Summary(BeaconBlock), // signing_root\r\n  state_root: Summary(BeaconState), // hash_tree_root\r\n  ...\r\n}\r\n```",
